snippet.title: Live Coding: Stripe Payment API
snippet.description:
Let's explore the Stripe payment API. It is supposed to have industry-leading documentation and be the easiest platform to work with. Let's find out!

Let's explore the Braintree payment API for selling products and subscriptions. Braintree accepts PayPal, Venmo, credit cards, Apple Pay, and many more!
